# CODSOFT-
this task of making to-do -list i have implemented css,html,and javascript for the functions like edit ,delete, add task by user  event listener and javascript code scripts
the following functionalities you will find in it 
Features
Add tasks to your to-do list.
Edit existing tasks.
Delete tasks.
Tasks are stored in local storage.


Getting Started
1-Clone the repository to your local machine using: 
git clone https://github.com/alishbasoomro17@gmail.com/CODSOFT.git
2-Navigate to the project directory:
cd CODSOFT
3-Open the index.html file in your web browser to start using the to-do list app.

Usage
Enter a task in the input field and click "Add Task" to add it to your list.

To edit a task, click the "Edit" button next to the task, and a prompt will appear to edit the task's text.

To delete a task, click the "Delete" button next to the task.

Tasks are stored in local storage, so you can close the browser and come back later to find your tasks still available.
